      "advancement": "spectrum:unlocks/equipment/lucky_pickaxe",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier1/tools/lucky_pickaxe",
      "text": "黄玉的$(c_yellow)能量$(), 让我能压榨出原矿里最后一点矿石$(br)$(c_yellow)$(bold)时运III$()."
    },
    {
      "type": "spectrum:pedestal_crafting",
      "advancement": "spectrum:unlocks/equipment/razor_falchion",
      "recipe": "spectrum:pedestal/tier1/tools/razor_falchion",
      "text": "短而锋利的刀片使它成为致命武器，但耐用性很拉跨.$(br)$(c_magenta)$(bold)抢夺III$()."
